name: TT-6
Lore: 'Primary command liaison transport. Contains the majority of officer battle druids. Has priority to unload as soon as the area is secured. Enclosed.',
Text: 'May add 7 passengers. Once per turn, may deploy a battle droid leader to same site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 if your AAT or STAP present).',
